{"tid":1073581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"將來得部手機吊吊揈咩都唔使開就可以登機？日本航空&KDDI話你聽5G嘅真實例子","createTime":"2019-03-22T19:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T12:30:31.000Z","uid":11598,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c5b8b74b5009d9bd116175fbe051d8c4e05c0cb","tid":1073581,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T19:03:43.000Z","msg":"次世代移動通信システム「5G」を使って飛行機への搭乗時に航空券を出す手間を解消する実証実験が行われました。 このシステムは特定の位置に照射しやすい5Gの電波を搭乗ゲート付近だけに出していて、搭乗用の専用アプリを入れたタブレット端末をバッグに入れていても正確に検知します。<br />\n<br />\n利用次世代移動通信系統「5G」技術，將來搭飛機嗰陣唔使再拎張機票出嚟咁麻煩喇。<br />\n最近日本航空就同KDDI整咗個原型出嚟，利用咗5G技術、係模擬登機閘口發射只會照射到特定位置嘅5G電波，只需要喺平板電腦先安裝咗專用嘅App就可以認證到你，而且就算部機擺喺背囊入邊都可以正確偵測到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/VBp1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FVBp1H.png&h=a19106e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只需要預先安裝咗App係部機到就OK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">チケット ：機票</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/VBL9x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FVBL9x.jpg&h=90d69d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就咁行埋去個閘口到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/VBQfV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FVBQfV.png&h=7e0c61ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5G電波只會射落個閘口（個人）附近嘅有限範圍之內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就可以偵測到條友部Tablet <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/VBcl2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FVBcl2.png&h=d3851771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個技術希望可以紓緩登記閘口嘅擠擁，同埋啲Staff唔使咁大壓力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過暫時都仲係實驗階段，未有真正落場嘅時間表  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n<br />\n而家日本仔就話俾你聽連QR Code check in 都已經過時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至NFC 都已經唔夠快，個快唔係講緊個資料傳送速度<br />\n而係講緊點樣可以幫人慳到時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真正活用科技 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那班傻閪仲喺度拎住5g 點快點勁 又iot 又乜得個吹字<br />\n老老柒柒 比啲實用到嘅例子嚟先得㗎<br />\n而家日本仔就好具體咁證明咗 5G 嘅實用性<br />\n將來可能唔淨止飛機閘口<br />\n分分鐘搭JR 連Suica都唔駛啪，直接掂行掂過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IF7yOqiyfTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIF7yOqiyfTk&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD13wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=6c564357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IF7yOqiyfTk</a>"},{"pid":"c979f69045275224696ec0ca0ced87aef97e982b","tid":1073581,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T19:04:26.000Z","msg":"反觀華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw巴士又no sleep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7295aafb7793cc7c86d5bda81be257f66ce8754a","tid":1073581,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c979f69045275224696ec0ca0ced87aef97e982b","tid":1073581,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T19:04:26.000Z","msg":"反觀華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s